sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant Client
  participant AuthController
  participant AuthService
  participant UserRepo as UserRepository
  participant PasswordEncoder
  participant EmailSvc as EmailVerificationService
  participant EmailTokenRepo as EmailVerificationTokenRepository
  participant JwtService
  participant RefreshRepo as RefreshTokenRepository

  rect rgb(245, 245, 255)
  Note over Client,AuthController: Register Flow
  Client->>AuthController: POST /api/auth/register (email, username, password)
  AuthController->>AuthService: register(...)
  AuthService->>UserRepo: existsByEmailOrUsername
  Note over AuthService: Eğer kullanıcı varsa hata döner (409).
  AuthService->>PasswordEncoder: encode(password)
  AuthService->>UserRepo: saveAndFlush(new user)
  AuthService->>EmailSvc: createVerificationToken(email)
  EmailSvc->>EmailTokenRepo: save(token)
  AuthService-->>AuthController: UserDto
  AuthController-->>Client: 200 + user bilgisi
  end

  rect rgb(245, 255, 245)
  Note over Client,AuthController: Login Flow
  Client->>AuthController: POST /api/auth/login (email, password)
  AuthController->>AuthService: login(...)
  AuthService->>UserRepo: findByEmail
  AuthService->>PasswordEncoder: matches(password)
  Note over AuthService: Email doğrulanmadıysa 401 döner.
  AuthService->>JwtService: generateAccessToken + generateRefreshToken
  AuthService->>RefreshRepo: save(hashed refresh token)
  AuthService-->>AuthController: AuthenticatedUserDto
  AuthController-->>Client: 200 + access/refresh token
  end

  rect rgb(255, 245, 245)
  Note over Client,AuthController: Email Verification Flow
  Client->>AuthController: GET /api/auth/verify?token=...
  AuthController->>EmailSvc: verifyEmail(token)
  EmailSvc->>EmailTokenRepo: findByToken
  Note over EmailSvc: Token kullanılmamış ve süresi geçmemiş olmalı.
  EmailSvc->>EmailTokenRepo: save(usedAt = now)
  EmailSvc->>UserRepo: save(hasVerifiedEmail = true)
  AuthController-->>Client: 200 (verified)
  end
